{"tid":2211534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港聞專題︰榮光信物 手足寄意","createTime":"2020-09-21T07:48:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T07:49:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bac2f0f0e78865a86f76c06920788b24b51db7cb","tid":2211534,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:48:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/27JDPTDJNJCSPHF4MGJKOUYSIU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2F27JDPTDJNJCSPHF4MGJKOUYSIU%2F&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZoqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=60a825b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200921%2F27JDPTDJNJCSPHF4MGJKOUYSIU%2F&h=0f147493\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200921/27JDPTDJNJCSPHF4MGJKOUYSIU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港聞專題︰榮光信物 手足寄意<br />\n<br />\n時近中秋，我們又再想起革命。元朝末年，一介平民朱元璋有感於極權暴政，聯合義士起義，光復中國。民間相傳，軍師劉伯溫提議於月餅偷藏寫上「八月十五夜起義」的紙條，結果民眾和應，成功推翻殘暴政權。公元2020年，月餅的意義在香港再次光復。今年中秋，過往被老牌連鎖餅家壟斷月餅市場的畫面已不復見，80多間黃店加入戰場，以月餅明志，回饋手足。從此，月餅不再只是送禮佳品，更是榮光信物。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：黃圈聯繫人：港人要自救<br />\n<br />\n記者：陳芷昕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wDJNhBhISQiGJcFwIrXVM2D71jI=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TG4GGQ4PCZBJPMPNSJKARLAMKI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwDJNhBhISQiGJcFwIrXVM2D71jI%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTG4GGQ4PCZBJPMPNSJKARLAMKI.jpg&h=74abc938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■K用心地以模子按壓餡料，一個個印有「我真係」、「好L」、「鍾意」、「香港」字句的奶黃月餅隨即成形。<br />\n<br />\n工場內飄盪着甜絲絲的奶黃味，和少男少女的歡笑聲。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，用模子按壓餡料，一個個寫上「我真係」、「好L」、「鍾意」、「香港」等字句的奶黃月餅隨即現形。<br />\n<br />\n這樣的成果絕對得來不易。苦練近兩個月，K屢次失敗，幾近崩潰。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。她從未輸給警察，永遠成功在戰場上全身而退，如今卻偏偏輸給了月餅。<br />\n<br />\n平日在家中只會煮即食麵的K，今日在廚房工作，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。久後，手足之間終建立互信，「試過同同事傾偈，傾傾吓先發現原來大家曾經喺同一時間出現喺同一地方，可能大家擦身而過好多次，但唔識大家，𠵱家竟然出現喺同一個地方，真係緣份！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/czikM5VLBrzLYvCIX0QPMydQ03w=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZFUOVG6BSFHXVPQOIC5KAO34YA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FczikM5VLBrzLYvCIX0QPMydQ03w%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZFUOVG6BSFHXVPQOIC5KAO34YA.jpg&h=95edeabe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Dawn Kitchen的「迷你金沙奶黃月餅」和「迷你低糖蛋黃白蓮蓉月餅」一套8個 $248。持本報報頭乙個可減$10，兩個可減$20，如此類推。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/dWUp-Tyzetlq5SPUPSlsRkKwuE0=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/V3XHIT4OQVEGNI43NPSB46N27Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FdWUp-Tyzetlq5SPUPSlsRkKwuE0%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FV3XHIT4OQVEGNI43NPSB46N27Y.jpg&h=a71f683f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n                               <br />\n<br />\n你快樂所以我快樂<br />\n<br />\n基於共同的政治理念和抗爭經歷，這十多位少男少女建立起深厚的友誼。因為資歷最長而被眾人笑稱為「大家姐」的K，留下非因愛上烘焙，而是純粹因為開心：「我哋真係一家人咁咩都會傾，我連感情問題都會搵媽媽傾！」<br />\n<br />\nK口中的「媽媽」，是手足廚房的負責人Sara。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。至今年2月，她正式成立手足廚房，高峯期時曾聘請40多名抗爭者工作，當中最年輕的年僅16、17歲，也有因被捕而失業的手足。<br />\n<br />\n44歲、本身育有一子一女的Sara，與一眾年輕手足打成一片，毫無隔閡，甚至將他們視如己出。他們出去「發夢」，她一定要他們向她報平安。他們受傷了，她就帶他們去看醫生。他們與家人因為政見不同而嘈吵，她就充當樹洞助他們修補關係，「我都做咗人哋阿媽，見到佢哋咁我都會肉赤」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n烘焙媽媽：建立手足的家<br />\n<br />\n手足廚房能否繼續支撐下去，也是未知之數。這裏僅靠Sara一人苦苦經營，本來生意尚可，獨門秘方「催淚彈味曲奇」尤受客人支持。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n自7月起，有黃店請手足廚房製作月餅，連同寫上打氣字句的明信片，寄送予流亡台灣的抗爭者，並在本地黃店發售。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，她對手足致以最高評價：「唔係個個一開始都做得好好，佢哋都會發吓脾氣，但唞完又會繼續。可能我哋嘅月餅係肉酸少少，但佢哋一定係好用心咁整！」<br />\n<br />\n對於月餅的銷情，Sara沒有多想，只希望可以一直守住手足廚房：「見到佢哋咁開心咁安樂，就會想繼續做落去，好似一個屋企咁，佢哋鍾意幾時返嚟都得。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FPMric0nb2gIuQEMy2x0GvENXFk=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WWWBXTUJ3VHXFHRQXBS4EIYMHI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFPMric0nb2gIuQEMy2x0GvENXFk%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWWWBXTUJ3VHXFHRQXBS4EIYMHI.jpg&h=865e6281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■連同寫有打氣字句的明信片，將會寄到台灣抗爭者的手上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/thyqcexbOoI9z8WTuArSyrni-JE=/1438x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PQ2LB4XCIBBNTK2I4HOPUAUGW4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FthyqcexbOoI9z8WTuArSyrni-JE%3D%2F1438x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPQ2LB4XCIBBNTK2I4HOPUAUGW4.jpg&h=f58040a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■沒有烘焙經驗的手足們，由零開始跟Sara學習製作月餅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/zs9KPWHXJqe3boiXm1PTliCdE3s=/2035x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ETBBWBUDG5FWBO34LHPHGRV6MU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fzs9KPWHXJqe3boiXm1PTliCdE3s%3D%2F2035x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FETBBWBUDG5FWBO34LHPHGRV6MU.jpg&h=92c6d8d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■屢次失敗的K，當餡料報廢時更會暴走洩忿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5cKtHxuyaKR7mZhbA3eCiJaJBgA=/2032x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BWLY4V4PJZEP5FWPWTQP63S2ZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5cKtHxuyaKR7mZhbA3eCiJaJBgA%3D%2F2032x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBWLY4V4PJZEP5FWPWTQP63S2ZE.jpg&h=69643594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■特訓過後，Sara對手足們的用心及堅持，均致以最高評價。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GzXZbFF3yCAA6uXErma0kJO3Az0=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/E2X5CRVAS5CWHCPS7AH2PGMJQY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGzXZbFF3yCAA6uXErma0kJO3Az0%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FE2X5CRVAS5CWHCPS7AH2PGMJQY.jpg&h=cb0dd501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■每張寄到台灣的明信片，都是手足們親自落墨，寫下個人心意。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pq75Y6wtwBPcMMaMZ3JVvcGYw44=/2031x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TETNF35WVBAOFETHIJTEIRQGBE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fpq75Y6wtwBPcMMaMZ3JVvcGYw44%3D%2F2031x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTETNF35WVBAOFETHIJTEIRQGBE.jpg&h=5604d3e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■Sara首次製作如此龐大數量的月餅，自言磨合亦需時。"},{"pid":"12418ebdd4569f5df030381cfdc61506657a6f4a","tid":2211534,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T07:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}